Mr. Roger N. FarahRalph Lauren Corp.New York, NYIn present position since 2000. Previously was chairman of Venator Group Inc. from 1994-2000 and as its CEO from 1994-1999. From July 1994 to October 1994 was president and COO of R.H. Macy & Co. From 1991-1994 was chairman and CEO of Federated Merchandising Services, the central buying and product development arm of Federated Department Stores Inc. He had also held numerous senior positions with Rich's/Goldmith's Department Stores. Formerly spent 12 years at Saks Fifth Avenue Inc. Also is a director of Aetna Inc.2008 Second QuarterAdded to: Progressive Corp. - Maryland Village, OHProgressive provides personal and commercial automobile insurance and other specialty property-casualty insurance products. Revenues are $19 billion.
    














 















 








